Reconciliation.description:
The collection of operational serivces/functions offered by the operational facility

Examples: messages, capture, routines

date.description: The schedule for handling the warehoused transaction batch

Warehousing.description:
The collection of operational serivces/functions offered by the operational facility

Examples: messages, capture, routines

InboundACHTransactionBatchReference.description: Reference to an inbound ACH transaction batch

ACHPaymentTransactionReference.description: Reference to a ACH payment transaction - included in the batch

PaymentTransactionInitiatorReference.description: Reference to the originator of the payment transaction

PayerReference.description: Reference to the source of funds in the payment

PayerProductInstanceReference.description: Reference to the payer's account (source of funds)

PayeeProductInstanceReference.description: Reference to the payee's account (target for funds)

SpecialInstructions.description: Transaction specific clearing and settlement instructions if appropriate

DateType.description: Key date types included in the transaction (e.g. order, booking, execution, value date, interest bearing)

InboundACH.description:
The collection of operational serivces/functions offered by the operational facility

Examples: messages, capture, routines

CorrespondentBankReference.description: Reference to the correspondent bank referenced in the ACH transaction

CorrespondentBankClearingAgreementRefere.description: Reference to the clearing agreement between bank and clearing house - includes schedule, limits

CorrespondentBankClearingAgreementSettle.description: Customer specific default settlement instruction e.g. to handle netting arrangements

MirrorNostroAccountReference.description: Account used central bank clearing reconciliations

ClearingandSettlement.description:
The collection of operational serivces/functions offered by the operational facility

Examples: messages, capture, routines

OutboundACHTransactionBatchReference.description: Reference to the batch ACH record
